OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA largely dry day with plenty
OL,6,Fof sunshine and feeling warm.
OL,7,
OL,8,CTonight:FA dry and warm evening with
OL,9,Fsome late sunny then clear spells.
OL,10,FGenerally cloudier across Argyll with
OL,11,Fthe risk of mist and fog for western
OL,12,Fcoasts.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTuesday:FEarly morning patchy cloud
OL,15,Fclearing to leave a dry day with
OL,16,Fplenty of warm sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
